{"tid":2450412,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（左膠賣國）未受中美角力影響 美行去年投入中國數十億美元","createTime":"2021-03-17T11:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T11:15:51.000Z","uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b14963c0b95d2676da1d885dbf38c2ae2e69e7cb","tid":2450412,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:06:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2903603/未受中美角力影響%20美行去年投入中國數十億美元\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2903603%2F%E6%9C%AA%E5%8F%97%E4%B8%AD%E7%BE%8E%E8%A7%92%E5%8A%9B%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF%2520%E7%BE%8E%E8%A1%8C%E5%8E%BB%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%95%E5%85%A5%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%81%E5%84%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%85%83&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTwpem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=89429c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2903603/未受中美角力影響%20美行去年投入中國數十億美元</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cf2Lipi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCf2Lipi.png&h=8d581f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道引述高盛的文件顯示，其「交叉貨幣餘額」（cross currency outstandings）去年在中國增長33%，至175億美元，包含現金、提供給公司和政府實體的融資等廣泛內容。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，高盛和花旗集團（Citigroup Inc.）、摩根大通（JPMorgan）、美國銀行（Bank of America）和摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）此美國五大銀行，合計敞口為778億美元，按年增長10%。"},{"pid":"0f1389a3feb457fd7f6421849a7a21e438948c6d","tid":2450412,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"投資銀行死都要痴埋支那市場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9640e0e761db0c830eb27ac859cda00ea9a32c42","tid":2450412,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0f1389a3feb457fd7f6421849a7a21e438948c6d","tid":2450412,"uid":66087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"投資銀行死都要痴埋支那市場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T11:15:51.000Z","msg":"Ipo<i